@startuml Recruiter_Matching

title Recruiter - Candidate Matching (Module E)

actor Recruiter as "👔 Nhà Tuyển Dụng"

rectangle "MATCHING" {
    usecase "Get Candidate\nRecommendations" as E1
    usecase "Calculate Match\nScore" as E3
}

Recruiter --> E1: 1. Get recommendations
E1 --> E3: 2. Check match score

note right of E1
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
